    <time_frame>Stool sample will be collected prior to initiation of bowel preparation for colonoscopy.</time_frame>
    <description>The outcomes are co-primary. Biomarkers under evaluation include differential methylation of nucleic acids and altered expression of proteins in stool from subjects at average risk or increased risk for development of colorectal cancer at the pre-intervention stage.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
